name: Applicative
body:
### What is Applicative?

We are a small team of passionate people who always dream of making people's life better. We believe in fast prototyping and iteration, we believe in scratching our own itch.

### What are we doing now?

We wouldn't say:) But you will know if you are interested, eventually. Wait for a couple weeks/months and come back to see!
